sec.p:
The model of ventricle is presented by cylindrical syringe and such model is convenient for our speculations due to coincidence of numerical values:


- of the distance of travel of the piston l (the size in 1-dimensional space) and the volume V (the size in 3-dimensional space);

- of linear velocity U of rectilinear motion of the piston and the volume flow rate Q cased by the motion of the piston.
